Definition: of worldwide scope or applicability
Example: an issue of cosmopolitan import; the shrewdest political and ecumenical comment of our time- Christopher Morley; universal experience
Synonyms: ecumenical, oecumenical, general, universal, verb, communication, universalize, noun, object, universe, attribute, universality, worldwide, world-wide, of, scope, or, applicability, an, issue, import, the, shrewdest, political, and, comment, our, time, -, Christopher, Morley, experience
Category: adj.all
